Package com.oracle.coherence.concurrent.executor

Interface PortableCollector<T,​A,​R>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of input elements to the reduction operation
    A - the mutable accumulation type of the reduction operation (often hidden as an implementation detail)
    R - the result type of the reduction operation
    All Superinterfaces:
    PortableObject, Serializable, Task.Collector<T,​A,​R>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCollector, TaskCollectors.CountCollector, TaskCollectors.FirstOfCollector, TaskCollectors.LastOfCollector, TaskCollectors.ListOfCollector, TaskCollectors.SetOfCollector
    public interface PortableCollector<T,​A,​R>
extends Task.Collector<T,​A,​R>, PortableObject
    A portable Task.Collector; a convenience interface for implementations having no properties to serialize.
    Since:
    21.12
    Author:
